1
00:00:00,424 --> 00:00:04,948
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,948 --> 00:00:10,452
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,452 --> 00:00:16,880
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:21,360
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,360 --> 00:00:25,808
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,808 --> 00:00:30,719
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,719 --> 00:00:34,768
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,768 --> 00:00:39,303
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,303 --> 00:00:43,600
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:48,365
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,365 --> 00:00:51,856
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,856 --> 00:00:55,536
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,182 --> 00:01:00,560
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:03,248
=Episode 31=

15
00:01:08,919 --> 00:01:12,725
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

16
00:01:12,725 --> 00:01:18,065
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

17
00:01:18,065 --> 00:01:25,128
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

18
00:01:25,128 --> 00:01:30,048
♪Anything I say can't fully describe♪

19
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:33,633
Yes, I do.

20
00:01:33,633 --> 00:01:35,833
What? I didn't ask you.

21
00:01:36,166 --> 00:01:39,100
It's so dreamy. Please look over here.

22
00:01:39,733 --> 00:01:42,066
Look at me. So amazing.

23
00:01:42,066 --> 00:01:44,266
You're really beautiful. Look here.

24
00:01:45,333 --> 00:01:47,399
Am I pretty? Let me take a look.

25
00:01:48,192 --> 00:01:49,500
What do you think?

26
00:01:49,666 --> 00:01:51,233
You've made me look
so fat in the photos.

27
00:01:51,233 --> 00:01:52,200
Shoot my right side.

28
00:01:52,733 --> 00:01:54,433
OK. Come on.

29
00:01:54,433 --> 00:01:56,333
Let's take a few more, like this.

30
00:01:56,333 --> 00:01:57,766
Get closer.

31
00:02:00,133 --> 00:02:02,466
So pretty. Truly a good-looking couple.

32
00:02:03,233 --> 00:02:04,366
Let me take a look.

33
00:02:04,366 --> 00:02:05,733
Look. You look very good.

34
00:02:07,233 --> 00:02:10,033
Sir, shoot from this angle.
It looks good.

35
00:02:10,033 --> 00:02:11,366
OK.

36
00:02:11,366 --> 00:02:12,608
Hello?

37
00:02:14,866 --> 00:02:16,128
What?

38
00:02:24,233 --> 00:02:25,500
Do you have anything else to say?

39
00:02:29,166 --> 00:02:32,133
Mr. Lan and Mrs. Lan, calm down.

40
00:02:32,666 --> 00:02:34,766
OK. Since it's been found out,

41
00:02:35,133 --> 00:02:36,366
I have nothing more to say.

42
00:02:41,566 --> 00:02:44,733
You already have so many shares.
Why are you still insatiable?

43
00:02:46,566 --> 00:02:47,936
Because...

44
00:02:49,933 --> 00:02:52,066
I simply can't stand you hypocrites.

45
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,266
You're slandering us.

46
00:02:57,400 --> 00:03:00,333
And I've trusted you all these years.

47
00:03:03,333 --> 00:03:07,333
(Ultrasound Report)
This is Gu Qianqian's pregnancy report.

48
00:03:11,833 --> 00:03:13,184
What do you mean?

49
00:03:16,433 --> 00:03:17,333
And this.

50
00:03:18,266 --> 00:03:19,666
These medical reports

51
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:23,066
can prove that this is Mr. Lan's baby.

52
00:03:23,766 --> 00:03:25,000
Congratulations, Mr. Lan.

53
00:03:44,666 --> 00:03:47,900
What's with this? What's going on?

54
00:03:49,733 --> 00:03:50,733
I don't know.

55
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,784
Lan,

56
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,333
feeling so bad?

57
00:04:27,866 --> 00:04:31,733
Mr. Gu, why are you visiting so late?

58
00:04:33,266 --> 00:04:36,733
This is premarital pregnancy.
If it gets out,

59
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,900
what others must think of our family.

60
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,333
Yes, what they must think of us.

61
00:04:45,233 --> 00:04:47,466
As long as
my shares and position are retained,

62
00:04:47,533 --> 00:04:49,266
I can keep my mouth shut.

63
00:04:53,166 --> 00:04:54,100
Regarding the accounts,

64
00:04:55,533 --> 00:04:56,566
I'll let that thing slide.

65
00:04:59,166 --> 00:05:00,400
Keep your mouth shut.

66
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:03,700
How will you explain this?

67
00:05:06,233 --> 00:05:10,300
It's a misunderstanding. It must be.

68
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:18,304
(Chen's Grandpa)

69
00:05:20,066 --> 00:05:22,866
Hello, what's wrong?

70
00:05:23,666 --> 00:05:25,333
It's bad. Grandpa just
had a car accident.

71
00:05:25,333 --> 00:05:27,666
He's now being given first aid treatment
and may become a vegetable.

72
00:05:27,744 --> 00:05:28,480
Ah?

73
00:05:31,633 --> 00:05:33,024
Mom.

74
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,000
How could this happen?

75
00:05:45,233 --> 00:05:46,600
(I got you engaged to Miss Gu,)

76
00:05:47,233 --> 00:05:50,966
(hoping you'd have
an easy life after my death.)

77
00:05:53,233 --> 00:05:56,500
I'll take responsibility
for that. Please leave.

78
00:05:58,033 --> 00:06:00,266
Didn't you refuse to marry
my daughter before?

79
00:06:03,133 --> 00:06:04,466
How could you do that to her?

80
00:06:04,466 --> 00:06:06,000
I told you I'd take responsibility.

81
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,648
Please leave.

82
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,384
What a shame.

83
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,366
Hello.

84
00:06:28,366 --> 00:06:29,500
Young Master, what's wrong?

85
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:37,533
This is a lot like what happened
to my dad back in the day, right?

86
00:06:51,456 --> 00:06:52,966
Mom.

87
00:06:53,133 --> 00:06:54,366
Hmm?

88
00:06:54,366 --> 00:06:56,000
I have something to discuss with you.

89
00:06:56,866 --> 00:07:00,133
I know you accepted a job abroad, right?

90
00:07:01,566 --> 00:07:02,566
How did you know?

91
00:07:04,633 --> 00:07:07,400
No matter what, as long as you're happy,

92
00:07:08,566 --> 00:07:09,866
I'll support you.

93
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,933
I understand you.

94
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,733
Just come back when you have time.

95
00:07:19,733 --> 00:07:21,300
Ever since you started martial arts,

96
00:07:21,466 --> 00:07:24,700
we've had to spend a lot of time apart.

97
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,466
This is the longest
you've stayed at home.

98
00:07:31,333 --> 00:07:32,533
I'm sorry, Mom.

99
00:07:32,866 --> 00:07:34,666
What's there to apologize for?

100
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,700
Everyone has their own life.

101
00:07:37,833 --> 00:07:40,300
Just stay safe and healthy.

102
00:07:46,666 --> 00:07:48,266
When are you leaving?

103
00:07:49,866 --> 00:07:51,133
I'm leaving tomorrow.

104
00:07:51,133 --> 00:07:52,576
So soon.

105
00:07:55,233 --> 00:07:57,133
The new season is about to start.

106
00:07:57,666 --> 00:08:00,066
I need to hurry there
for the coaching assignment.

107
00:08:01,666 --> 00:08:04,066
I'll tell Xi'en
when she's back from work.

108
00:08:14,733 --> 00:08:18,200
I'm a bit tired.
I'll go back to my room to rest.

109
00:08:45,333 --> 00:08:46,300
Why are you here?

110
00:08:56,166 --> 00:08:57,100
We're here

111
00:08:58,133 --> 00:09:00,333
to deliver the invitation
to my wedding tomorrow.

112
00:09:03,734 --> 00:09:08,000
(Lan Chen, Gu Qianqian)

113
00:09:22,433 --> 00:09:25,733
You don't have to watch what you eat,
but you have to watch what you say.

114
00:09:29,433 --> 00:09:30,866
Still so rude.

115
00:09:31,933 --> 00:09:32,966
Don't you believe it?

116
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,533
Then come over tomorrow.

117
00:09:39,166 --> 00:09:40,966
I don't know what's gotten into you,

118
00:09:41,766 --> 00:09:42,733
but

119
00:09:43,933 --> 00:09:45,333
you are not welcome here.

120
00:09:46,366 --> 00:09:47,766
I'm serious.

121
00:09:48,333 --> 00:09:50,666
Tomorrow is Lan's big day.

122
00:09:51,233 --> 00:09:52,766
As his secretary,

123
00:09:54,033 --> 00:09:55,566
shouldn't you be by his side?

124
00:09:56,366 --> 00:09:57,800
No,

125
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,800
below the stage.

126
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,133
Leave now, or I won't be this friendly.

127
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:05,866
Just do it. Come on, kick here.

128
00:10:06,466 --> 00:10:07,600
Lan's baby.

129
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:23,100
Hahaha.

130
00:10:32,333 --> 00:10:33,300
I've said it.

131
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,700
There's nothing in this world

132
00:10:37,466 --> 00:10:39,000
that I want and can't get.

133
00:10:39,266 --> 00:10:41,433
And you.

134
00:10:41,433 --> 00:10:45,500
You're just
a minor chapter in his story.

135
00:10:51,566 --> 00:10:52,733
Miss Jin,

136
00:10:54,133 --> 00:10:55,680
don't do it.

137
00:10:59,247 --> 00:11:03,769
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

138
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:11,760
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

139
00:11:14,809 --> 00:11:20,633
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

140
00:11:20,633 --> 00:11:28,103
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

141
00:11:28,103 --> 00:11:31,584
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

142
00:11:31,584 --> 00:11:35,705
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

143
00:11:35,705 --> 00:11:37,401
♪Open my secret♪

144
00:11:37,401 --> 00:11:43,449
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

145
00:11:43,449 --> 00:11:47,321
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

146
00:11:47,321 --> 00:11:51,827
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

147
00:11:51,827 --> 00:12:00,537
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
